{"tid":838540,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"細行加息0.25厘狼過大行 三發鈔行齊加P息0.125厘","createTime":"2018-09-27T07:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T08:19:06.000Z","uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc79cfc8ee1e262cfc185c5f11f71806991baca","tid":838540,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"【新增影片●下午15時30分】<br />\n華僑永亨宣佈，上調最優惠利率(P)，由5.25厘增至5.5厘，加幅跑贏大行，明日起生效。 該行現時之港元儲蓄存款利率維持不變，至0.25厘。<br />\n華僑永亨銀行行政總裁藍宇鳴表示，一個月及三個月港元拆息自今年一月以來分別上升了108點子及97點子，存款成本因而上升。今次調高港元最優惠利率為對應市場息率上升及資金成本上漲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180927/58728252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728252&d=ponsyYfsuH7%2BR%2BoRpLuOk8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=30578ce7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F58728252&h=c85da731\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180927/58728252</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">加息加幾多係個別銀行決定, 所以匯豐今日加0.125唔代表佢之後唔會追加</span>"},{"pid":"7729507d90fba83c9bf153363db4064701a3c5f7","tid":838540,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"push"}]}